359
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,472
...Cooper-Smoot. alphabetical...

360
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:45,633
...and when we win the Nobel Prize.
you'll be back on top.

361
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:48,800
With all due respect. Dr. Cooper.
are you on crack?

362
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:54,915
Fine. Smoot-Cooper.

